Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.92,0:01:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.25,0:02:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在心情不好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.95,0:02:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再胡鬧的話我可不會手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.35,0:02:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼弱 少囂張了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.55,0:02:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放馬過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.35,0:02:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要打斷你的肋骨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後演奏出美妙的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.45,0:02:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來對付你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.35,0:02:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩腳被線…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要演奏出美妙的旋律了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,do
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.25,0:03:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,re
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.05,0:03:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底從什麼地方攻過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.25,0:03:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的骨頭發出來的聲音真低沉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.25,0:03:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓它更清脆一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.55,0:03:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:03:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是mi fa so三個音了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.95,0:04:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獅子連彈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音忍的誘惑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.05,0:04:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.95,0:04:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻 吃吧吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兒的叉燒面是最棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 今天我請客
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.25,0:04:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請女朋友吃飯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.15,0:04:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人很厲害嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.05,0:04:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女…你說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:04:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天和小櫻…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.30,0:04:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有重要的事要說…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是什麼女朋友呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.35,0:05:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.75,0:05:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 鳴人 我走神了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.05,0:05:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邊吃邊告訴我佐助的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.55,0:05:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然佐助讓我不要告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.35,0:05:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都因為那個大蛇丸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.25,0:06:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西老師都說沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.05,0:06:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想相信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.55,0:06:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 和我愛羅戰鬥的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.95,0:06:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.05,0:06:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的佐助和那時的表情一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.65,0:06:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.25,0:06:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最近也見過他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.95,0:06:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.65,0:06:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在尋找綱手婆婆的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.95,0:06:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.45,0:07:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對好色仙人和綱手婆婆兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他依然毫不遜色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.05,0:07:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個危險的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.35,0:07:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.45,0:07:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.95,0:07:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助不會被那種傢伙引誘的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.55,0:07:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不必這麼做就已經很強了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.45,0:07:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保證
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.85,0:08:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼需要這樣的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸大人真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不如君麻呂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.25,0:08:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果一直呆在這種垃圾一樣的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠只能做個普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.45,0:08:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會變強
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.65,0:08:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.95,0:08:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連彈明明全部命中了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可這傢伙根本毫髮無傷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.05,0:08:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和同伴們開心地玩忍者遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.15,0:08:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會一直腐朽下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來大蛇丸大人會賜予你力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果強行帶回去好像沒什麼意義
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.25,0:08:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你決定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:09:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸大人還真麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.35,0:09:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走還是不走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽快點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.25,0:09:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼弱的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.75,0:09:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還磨磨蹭蹭 真想殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.05,0:09:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試試看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.15,0:09:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然有咒印…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是你被大蛇丸大人看中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.85,0:09:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別亂用咒印
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.35,0:09:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像還沒能自由控制咒印嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果長時間持續解封狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.75,0:10:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咒印就會開始侵蝕身體
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.35,0:10:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還處在狀態一階段
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.95,0:10:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侵蝕的速度很慢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.95,0:10:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦被完全侵蝕的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會失去自我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠地…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然憑借咒印得到了力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.95,0:10:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與此同時也受到了大蛇丸大人的束縛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.15,0:10:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經沒有自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.75,0:10:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要得到些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.25,0:10:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必須捨棄一些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的目的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.25,0:10:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這溫暖的村子裡和同伴們互相慰藉傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.45,0:10:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你忘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇智波鼬的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.15,0:10:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘記你的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.35,0:10:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個村子對你來說只是個枷鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:11:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了斷你的那些無聊羈絆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來你就會得到更強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.75,0:11:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘記目的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎下次光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.45,0:11:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻 我送你回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.15,0:11:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.35,0:11:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.85,0:11:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走夜路可是很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.85,0:11:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼亮 不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.75,0:11:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.15,0:12:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我現在想一個人回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.25,0:12:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.05,0:12:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.95,0:13:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半夜三更的 你在這裡晃蕩什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出村子 一定會經過這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.55,0:13:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家睡覺去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.55,0:14:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.95,0:14:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼都不告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.55,0:14:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼每次有事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.36,0:14:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不願意告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.86,0:14:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為什麼非要告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都讓你別多管閒事了 別管我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只會惹佐助討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.35,0:14:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們成為下忍 被編在同一組的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.65,0:14:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡 頭一次與佐助獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.85,0:15:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我惹佐助生了很大的氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.65,0:15:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 那傢伙不是沒有父母嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人 沒有父母管教
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.25,0:15:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會這麼任性啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤獨…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.25,0:15:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是被父母訓斥的痛苦所能比擬的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.25,0:15:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.65,0:15:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很惹人厭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.85,0:15:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.75,0:15:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 已經是很久之前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 就是從那一天開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.25,0:15:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助和我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有鳴人 卡卡西老師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.65,0:16:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四個人一起執行各種任務
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.75,0:16:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很苦 很累
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.05,0:16:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這比什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:16:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…都開心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.95,0:17:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我知道佐助家族的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.55,0:17:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 復仇什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻無法讓任何人幸福起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.65,0:17:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.15,0:17:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助也好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.95,0:17:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.55,0:17:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你們不同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.25,0:17:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你們所走的道路不同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四個人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.05,0:17:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確 我也曾以為那就是自己的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.25,0:17:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四人在一起 我的心最終決定復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.85,0:17:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是為此而活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.85,0:18:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我無法變得像你和鳴人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.55,0:18:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助又要獨自走向孤單嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.65,0:18:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候你告訴我孤獨多麼痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我非常瞭解那種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.25,0:18:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有家人和朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.65,0:18:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.15,0:18:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是失去了佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.75,0:18:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.25,0:18:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與孤獨無異
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只不過各自邁向新的目標而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.85,0:18:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.65,0:18:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的真的非常喜歡佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.55,0:18:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果佐助能和我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.05,0:18:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決不會讓你後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都開開心心地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.35,0:18:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對會很幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.35,0:18:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了佐助 我什麼都會去做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.85,0:18:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 求你了 留下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.95,0:19:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會幫你復仇的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.05,0:19:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會想辦法幫你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.35,0:19:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 和我一起留下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不行的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.95,0:19:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就帶我一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.55,0:19:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然 很讓人討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.55,0:19:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.05,0:19:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再走一步 我就大叫了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.85,0:19:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.45,0:19:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.65,0:20:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等您很久了 佐助大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.65,0:20:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是吹的哪陣風
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.65,0:20:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當您踏出這座村子的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.45,0:20:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您就是我們的首領了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的無禮舉動 請您原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.35,0:20:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.45,0:20:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.75,0:21:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.92,0:22:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.25,0:22:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助到底在想什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.79,0:22:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太離譜了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.26,0:22:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算再怎麼不滿 也不能拋棄村子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.20,0:22:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.73,0:22:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼能讓他繼續為所欲為
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.97,0:22:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 不管他跑到天涯海角
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.77,0:22:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算拼上我的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.60,0:22:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要帶他回來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.04,0:23:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.80,0:23:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組成鐵壁陣式
